{"tid":498983,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"今晨做手術  黎瑞恩成功切除腹部","createTime":"2017-12-14T10:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T10:39:29.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a783966136a84b9ad5e761b53b2995d69f6e09","tid":498983,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"將於明年舉行演唱會的黎瑞恩（小恩子）日前才現身電視城演繹梅艷芳的金曲，但今日突傳來她入院的消息！據小恩子公司發言人表示：「小恩子最近唔舒服，經醫生檢查發現腹部有有一個正在擴大的腫瘤，醫生建議趁腫瘤尚細，進行切除手術。」 <br />\n<br />\n而小恩子今朝一早就在醫院接受手術，手術非常順利，在腹部成功取出一個小腫瘤，小恩子現正休息中，她向歌迷表示多謝大家關心及慰問。而小恩子更在其公司的官方社交網上載入院的照片，見戴上手術帽的她一臉愕然，表情很趣怪。"},{"pid":"4a1b7ba6660b7c59bb74335068e710a3877e04d4","tid":498983,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"一切都是神的安排"},{"pid":"af152dc375765ea777c1b2d147be48d621ae1b57","tid":498983,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:19:09.000Z","msg":"有飛賣未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698fe9116d12845f1502b2c47327d21cfb7de0a4","tid":498983,"uid":1187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:21:46.000Z","msg":"切除腹部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d73b48a021ce6116ca7896de56de6c8af4527e","tid":498983,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>切除腹部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87ffdb28b2e029c7691a522c76124eee77389e5","tid":498983,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"日本武士咩切腹"},{"pid":"4da6775eaa6c12057a02a912a1e29e20b3f6649e","tid":498983,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re